'''Ali Nemati''' ({{langx|fa|علی نعمتی}}, born 8 February 1996) is an Iranian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] club [[Foolad F.C.|Foolad]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].<ref>{{Soccerway|ali-nemati/501022}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.varzesh11.com/fa/soccer_club/teams/%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B4%DA%AF%D8%A7%D9%87_%D9%81%D9%88%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84_%D9%BE%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%87/272|title=Shahr Khodro F.C. {{!}} Varzesh11|website=www.varzesh11.com|language=fa|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927083419/http://www.varzesh11.com/fa/soccer_club/teams/%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B4%DA%AF%D8%A7%D9%87_%D9%81%D9%88%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84_%D9%BE%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%87/272|archive-date=2018-09-27|access-date=2020-01-04}}</ref>

== Club career ==
=== Persepolis ===
[[File:(Tehran) Persepolis F.C. v Al Nassr FC, 19 September 2023 16.jpg|thumb|Nemati and [[Cristiano Ronaldo]] before an [[AFC Champions League]] match in 2023]]
On 24 August 2021, Nemati signed a three-year contract with [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] champions [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]].<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-08-24|title=Persepolis complete signing of Ali Nemati|url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/464294/Persepolis-complete-signing-of-Ali-Nemati|access-date=2021-08-30|website=Tehran Times|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Padideh Defender Nemati Joins Persepolis - Sports news|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2021/08/25/2559893/padideh-defender-nemati-joins-persepolis|access-date=2021-08-30|website=Tasnim News Agency|language=en}}</ref>

==International career==
Nemati made his debut for the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]] on 10 October 2024 in a [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – AFC third round|World Cup qualifier]] against Uzbekistan at the [[Milliy Stadium]]. He played the full game in a 0–0 draw.<ref>{{cite web|work=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/710454/iran-uzbekistan|title=Uzbekistan v Iran game report|date=10 October 2024}}</ref>

== Style of play ==
A header defender with hard-working, aggressive,disciplined and hard-tackling style of play,Nemati had a powerful debute. While playing for Persepolis, after scoring 4 goals for the team, he mentioned as a good header with impressive ability to play in the [[Defender (association football)|left-back]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=پروازهای علی نعمتی برای فیکس شدن (عکس) |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1834540/%D9%BE%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B2%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C-%D9%86%D8%B9%D9%85%D8%AA%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D9%81%DB%8C%DA%A9%D8%B3-%D8%B4%D8%AF%D9%86-%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3 |access-date=2023-02-05 |website=ورزش سه |language=fa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=یحیی دفاع جدیدش را پیدا کرده؟ (عکس) |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1840186/%DB%8C%D8%AD%DB%8C%DB%8C-%D8%AF%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B9-%D8%AC%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D8%B4-%D8%B1%D8%A7-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D8%AF%D8%A7-%DA%A9%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%87-%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3 |access-date=2023-02-05 |website=ورزش سه |language=fa}}</ref>

